entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It appears as though the couple's daughters skipped out on the equestrian event which was also attended byKendall Jenner.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1269, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9923243138358113, \"rank\": 0.0077087461790254766, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlyn_Jenner\", \"score\": 0.9999999958247372, \"rank\": 4.1739875806437446e-09, \"text\": \"Jenner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlyn_Jenner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlyn_Jenner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mendes, who stepped back from acting in 2014 to focus on raising her daughters, and Gosling have kept their private life under the radar.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the 2024 Oscars, where Gosling was nominated in the Best Actor category, asource explainedthat the couple's \\\"most important job is their girls.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything else comes second.\\\"\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't thinking about kids before I met her, but after I met Eva, I realized that I just did not want to have kids without her,\\\" Gosling toldGQlast year.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And there were moments onThe Place Beyond the Pineswhere we were pretending to be a family, and I did not really want it to be pretend anymore.\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I realized that this would be a life I would be really lucky to have.\\\"\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}]